name: CryoCorp
description:
In the future, while the poor are
still buried and cremated, a new
class of elitists called the
Inmortalis have their bodies
frozen in stasis. Some do so to
live in the future, while others
await medicinal breakthroughs
to prolong life. This detested
sect are renowned for their
arrogance, for trying to cheat
death and their never ending
wealth, while the rest of society
simply try to stay alive.
